data.description: Colonial charm meets modern elegance in this Ford's Colony townhome overlooking the 16th fairway of the Blue Heron Course. A 2020 remodel brought new life to the first-floor primary suite, featuring a spacious bedroom, dual sink vanity, and a walk-in closet. The expansive kitchen, remodeled in 2020, stands as one of The Links' largest. Formal dining, breakfast nook, and a wood-burning fireplace in the living room offer perfect spaces for entertaining. Upstairs, two generously sized bedrooms, a full bathroom, and ample storage ensure comfort. A new heat pump in 2022 adds efficiency. The HOA handles exterior maintenance—siding, roof, landscaping—in a gated community. Live in luxury at 515 Dogleg Dr., where history and sophistication converge in Williamsburg. Available for VA assumption 2.25%. "Non-veterans may apply"
